      "title": "Pakistan floods death toll rises to 1,191",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to figures released by Pakistan's National Disaster Management Authority, the death toll from monsoon floods in Pakistan since June has reached 1,191.",
        "It said another 3,641 people were injured as heavy rains that affected more than 33 million people continued to lash parts of the country."
      ],
